May Emory https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/May_Emory 0 May Emory (1885-1948) was an American actress. She appeared in 28 films between 1915 and 1919. Some of her work from Teddy at the Throttle appears in the 1960 compilation When Comedy Was King.She was married to actor Harry Gribbon, brother of actor Eddie Gribbon.
